*portage-2.2.0_alpha101 (28 Apr 2012)

  28 Apr 2012; Dmitry 'daks' Fomenko <daks12@gmail.com>
  +portage-2.2.0_alpha101.ebuild:
  2.2.0_alpha101 add ver.2 patch for autopatching. Patches (files with
  .patch extension) are searched recursively from the folder
  ${PORTAGE_PATCHDIR}/${CATEGORY}/${PN} with all folders which name
  matching version of the package being installed separated by dot.
  For portage-2.2.0_alpha101 for example search will be performed in
  ${PORTAGE_PATCHDIR}/sys-apps/portage/
  ${PORTAGE_PATCHDIR}/sys-apps/portage/2/
  ${PORTAGE_PATCHDIR}/sys-apps/portage/2/2/
  ${PORTAGE_PATCHDIR}/sys-apps/portage/2/2/0_alpha101.

*portage-2.2.0_alpha100 (20 Apr 2012)

  20 Apr 2012; Dmitry 'daks' Fomenko <daks12@gmail.com>
  +portage-2.2.0_alpha100.ebuild:
  2.2.0_alpha100 add patch for autopatching. Need to set ${PORTAGE_PATCHDIR}
  variable in make.conf.
